      <title>雪佛龙以 65 亿美元出售加拿大油砂、页岩资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chevron-sells-oil-sands-and-shale-assets-to-cnr-for-6-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司同意以 65 亿美元的价格将其持有的部分油砂和页岩资产的股份出售给加拿大自然资源有限公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chevron-sells-oil-sands-and-shale-assets-to-cnr-for-6-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新考虑政策，关键美国债券收益率自 8 月以来首次触及 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份强劲的就业报告迫使交易员重新评估货币政策前景后，美国主要国债收益率回升至 4%，为 8 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铁矿石价格上涨，因预期中国将推出更多刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/iron-ore-pushes-higher-on-hopes-more-china-stimulus-is-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格上涨——延续两周的大幅上涨——因市场猜测中国最高经济规划者将于周二推出更多刺激措施。其他工业金属价格基本保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/iron-ore-pushes-higher-on-hopes-more-china-stimulus-is-coming</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风米尔顿横扫墨西哥湾，直逼佛罗里达州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/florida-faces-deadly-tropical-threat-in-hurricane-helene-s-wake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风米尔顿正向佛罗里达州前进，强度可能达到 4 级，并可能引发七年来最大规模的撤离，因为它的目标是该州的墨西哥湾沿岸和坦帕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/florida-faces-deadly-tropical-threat-in-hurricane-helene-s-wake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
